data.description: Nestled at the end of a peaceful Cul-de-Sac, within the secure gated neighborhood of Madison Colony in the heart of the master-planned Providence community, this three-bedroom, three-bathroom home boasts a spacious loft, offering a harmonious blend of spacious living and comfort. The kitchen features custom quartz countertops and matching backsplash and ample cabinet space. With a large primary bedroom and primary bath offering both a separate tub and a shower for relaxation and convenience with a generous walk-in closet. With one bedroom and a full bath on the lower level, you have an ideal space for guests or family members seeking privacy. The fully landscaped backyard is a serene haven with a covered patio for outdoor enjoyment. Enjoy living next to a charming community park in a secure, gated community and make this home your new sanctuary. This home is offered by an owner licensee, ensuring a smooth process.
